dct_description_sm: By Edwd. Weller, F.R.G.S. ; Weekly Dispatch Atlas, 139, Fleet Street ; E. Weller, Lithogr. ; Engraved by Edwd. Weller, 34, Red Lion Square.
Bar scales in English and Geographical miles.
Illustration at head of title: "The Dispatch Atlas."
Shows waterways, regional and tribal names, towns and villages.
Textual descrptions, such as "Grassy Plains," and "Flat & Marshy."
Bottom right margin : "124"; taken from (Cassells?) "Weekly Dispatch Atlas" of unknown year.
Lake Tanganyika present on map; with only southern parts of Lake Victoria (unnamed) and Lake Nyassa (named) shown.
